Diamondskin<br>
Basic description: Creates a damage-absorbing protective force field around you.<br>
Raw data: <!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://lucy.fnord.net/spell.html?id=394&source=Live">lucy.fnord.net/spell.html...ource=Live</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br>
Graffë's notes: If you are attracting the attention to use it, you should probably change your tactics. A wizard of your power should not need it. It's nice to have just in case, though.<br>
Whizbang's notes: While this is an upgrade, in my opinion, the steep hike in price isn't merited by the added protection. I suggest sticking with Steelskin unless you have platinum burning a hole in your pocket.<br>
